</svg></span></span></a></span> <span class=3D"bc-delimiter">/</span> <span=
 class=3D"kadence-bread-current">Yarn Calculators</span></div></nav><h1 cla=
ss=3D"entry-title">Yarn Calculators</h1></header><!-- .entry-header -->
<div class=3D"entry-content single-content">
<p>We are in the process of creating easy calculators that will help all cr=
ocheters and knitters effectively change any pattern. These tools will work=
 on any pattern, and not just those found within <a href=3D"https://easycro=
chet.com/all-free-crochet-patterns/">Easy Crochet=E2=80=99s archives</a>. <=
/p>
<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Crochet Calculators</h2>
<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/blanket-crochet-resizing=
-calculator/"><strong>Blanket Resizing Calculator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 He=
lps you size (or resize) crochet blanket patterns. It lists total stitch co=
unts, rows, and yardage for multiple blanket sizes.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/c2c-crochet-blanket-size=
-calculator/"><strong>C2C Blanket Sizing Calculator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 =
This simple calculator helps you determine the final estimated size of a C2=
C blanket, along with how many squares are needed to achieve that particula=
r size.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/crochet-scarf-calculator=
/"><strong>Scarf Calculator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 Generate a sample scarf =
pattern with appropriate yardage for any crocheted scarf size.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Knitting Calculators</h2>
<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/balanced-increase-decrea=
se-knit-calculators/"><strong>Balanced Increase &amp; Decrease</strong></a>=
 =E2=80=93 Use these calculators to determine how to increase or decrease e=
venly across your row or round of knitting.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">General Calculators</h2>
<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/yarn-substitutio=
n/">Yarn Substitution</a></strong> =E2=80=93 This tool will determine if yo=
u can swap one type and brand of yarn with another. We calculate the relati=
ve weight per length for two yarn skeins and then compare the differences.<=
/li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/how-much-yarn-do-i-have/=
"><strong>Yarn Stash Calculator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 This will help estim=
ate how much yardage you have in your stash by weight.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/yarn-remaining-in-skein/=
"><strong>How Much Yarn is Remaining in a Skein?</strong></a> =E2=80=93 Thi=
s calculator shows how much yarn is left inside a partially used skein of y=
arn based on its weight in grams or ounces.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/project-yardage-calculat=
or/"><strong>Project Yardage Calculator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 Find out how=
 much yarn you used in a project with this simple crochet yardage chart too=
l.</li>
<li><strong><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/striped-pattern-=
generator/">Random Stripe Pattern Generator</a></strong> =E2=80=93 Use this=
 tool to create random stripe patterns for blankets, hats and more in knitt=
ing &amp; crochet.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/multiples-calculator/"><=
strong>Multiples Generator</strong></a> =E2=80=93 Use this handy table to g=
enerate multiples of any number. This is especially helpful for resizing cr=
ochet projects that require multiples of a certain amount.</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/calculators/us-metric-yarn-conversio=
n/"><strong>US to Metric (and back) Conversions</strong></a> =E2=80=93 Conv=
ert your yarn requirements that are either in grams or meters to ounces and=
 yards=E2=80=A6 and vice versa!</li>
</ul>
<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Crochet Sizing Charts</h2>
<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/crochet-scarf-size-chart/">Scarf Siz=
es</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/crochet-hat-size-chart/">Hat Sizes</=
a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/blanket-sizes-chart/">Blanket Sizes<=
/a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/crochet-mitten-glove-sizing-chart-gu=
ide/">Mitten &amp; Glove Sizes</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://easycrochet.com/crochet-hook-sizes/">Hook Sizes</a><=
/li>
</ul>
</div><!-- .entry-content -->
